T1  - Institutional voids and business group dynamics: Evidence from judicial reform in China11We gratefully acknowledge financial support from the National Natural Science Foundation of China (No. 71772039)，National Social Science Foundation of China (No. 21&ZD144), the Fundamental Research Funds for the Central Universities in UIBE (CXTD14–01), the Postgraduate Innovative Research Fund of University of International Business and Economics (No. 202509), and Taishan Young Talent Scholar Project of Shandong Province (No. 20221116).
